so much so that I'm going to read it again,

02:00:01.660 --> 02:00:05.500
because this is really what it means to be mentally healthy.

02:00:05.500 --> 02:00:07.700
Again, the generative drive is our desire

02:00:07.700 --> 02:00:09.660
to create, build and contribute to the world

02:00:09.660 --> 02:00:12.780
in a meaningful way and appreciate the process to get there.

02:00:12.780 --> 02:00:15.580
It is the core feature of our mental health.

02:00:15.580 --> 02:00:17.940
So being able to access that generative drive

02:00:17.940 --> 02:00:20.420
on a regular basis is really what this thing

02:00:20.420 --> 02:00:23.020
that we call mental health is all about.

